	dprr:hasNoteText "Served under Q. Caecilius Metellus (87), probably as quaestor or legatus, in 68- 67 (Cic. Planc. 27, no title preserved). See Syme, Historia 13, 1964, 156-166, esp. 160-161-RP 2.605-616, esp. 610. Listed wrongly in RE as Cn. (Appuleius) Saturninus, no. 27.\n" .
